 thing at all! Every money-market fund just lists all of its holdings, by s=
ize and issuer and CUSIP! Tether has broken new ground in the concept of co=
mmercial-paper privacy rights! But, why?</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ev=
erything in this interview melted my brain. Another favorite came at around=
 the 13-minute mark, when GC Stuart Hoegner says =E2=80=9Cwe maintain cash,=
 for example, that is many multiples above our single biggest redemption th=
us far, as well as above our biggest 24-hour period of redemptions,=E2=80=
