 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> wrote last month</a>=C2=A0that =E2=80=
=9CI think of stablecoins as sort of the lobby of the casino that is crypto=
