reak from betting on Bitcoin without actually leaving the casino.=E2=80=9D =
If that=E2=80=99s the main use case then the worst thing that happens, in a=
 run on Tether, is that a bunch of gamblers lose their money; that is bad f=
or them but I am not sure how it is a=C2=A0<em>systemic=C2=A0</em>problem. =
As <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24525843.267046=
/aHR0cHM6Ly9kaWZmLnN1YnN0YWNrLmNvbS9wL2Jhbmtpbmctd2FudHMtdG8tYmUtZnJlZS1idX=
